<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-AO" data-theme="dark">
<head>
    <%- include('../../partials/head-meta', { title: 'Página Não Encontrada', moduleStyle: 'auth' }) %>
    <style>
        .error-page-wrapper {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #1a1a2e 0%, #0b0b12 100%);
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 10rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: -5px;
        }
        .error-illustration {
            max-width: 300px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(255, 59, 92, 0.2));
        }
        .error-message h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .error-message p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
        }
        .btn-back-home {
            padding: 12px 35px;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-radius: 50px;
            background: var(--primary-color);
            border: none;
            color: white;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 59, 92, 0.3);
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .btn-back-home:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            background: var(--primary-hover);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255, 59, 92, 0.5);
        }
        .glitch-effect {
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        @keyframes glitch {
            0% { transform: translate(0); }
            20% { transform: translate(-2px, 2px); }
            40% { transform: translate(-2px, -2px); }
            60% { transform: translate(2px, 2px); }
            80% { transform: translate(2px, -2px); }
            100% { transform: translate(0); }
        }
        .error-code:hover {
            animation: glitch 0.3s infinite;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-page-wrapper">
        <div class="container animate-up">
            <div class="error-code-container">
                <div class="error-code">404</div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Tech/Anime Illustration (Using a placeholder for the missing actual asset) -->
            <div class="mb-4">
                <i class="bi bi-shield-slash text-dim" style="font-size: 5rem;"></i>
            </div>

            <div class="error-message">
                <h1>Área Restrita ou Inexistente</h1>
                <p>Parece que o caminho que tentaste aceder foi selado ou nunca existiu no catálogo do Otaku Clash Angola. Verifica o URL ou volta para a segurança do painel.</p>
                
                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-center gap-3">
                    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-back-home">
                        <i class="bi bi-grid-1x2-fill"></i> Voltar ao Dashboard
                    </a>
                    <button class="btn-oc btn-oc-outline px-4" onclick="history.back()">
                        <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> Página Anterior
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-5 pt-5 border-top border-secondary border-opacity-10">
                <img src="/assets/img/logo-icon.png" width="40" style="opacity: 0.3;" alt="OC Logo">
                <div class="text-dim small mt-2">© 2026 Otaku Clash Angola Team</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Core Scripts -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        // Log local for debugging in admin panel
        console.warn('[System] Error 404: Path not found - ' + window.location.pathname);
    </script>
</body>
</html>